                             MSPB PRIVACY POLICY

   The Merit Systems Protection Board will collect no personal information
   about you when you visit our website unless you choose to provide that
   information. The only information collected is the visitor's Internet
   domain and Internet Protocol address, the type of browser and operating
   system used to access the site, and the date and time the visitor
   accessed the site.

   Last Updated: January 29, 2002
